  "text": "11 Local invasion and various histopathological features can be suggestive; however, these features are not widely accepted and there is a need for the development of more sensitive and specific diagnostic means. [CITATION_1] 13 This said, the lack of firm predictors of malignancy, coupled with the variable course of this rare disease, make life-long followup of patients with chromaffin-cell tumors mandatory.",
